                                <ns0:support><ns0:p>Plinth (support for a stele) with mouldings top and bottom, of the local sandstone; the upper moulding is damaged, principally at the corners. The plinth is the left one of a pair mounted on a single base, classified as an epitymbion of type C.</ns0:p>
